public long importTrigger(java.lang.String sSettingsFile)
                   throws ScriptingException
User can specify a previously exported trigger properties XML file to setup a trigger. The file should be exported from script console window, not from UBM.

Parameters:
sSettingsFile - is the file that would have been exported by CCS for a given trigger job. It should include absolute path description.
Returns:
Trigger ID to be used to enable/disable trigger.
Throws:
ScriptingException
